{"tid":2262974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中原香港第3季營業額10.5億元   錄得盈利　向員工發放花紅","createTime":"2020-10-29T13:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T11:04:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5c9d90eac9e4b302571dc17f5dced2510f518e8f","tid":2262974,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:37:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557359-20201029.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557359-20201029.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KikzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=2d4d6ba2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557359-20201029.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7e5abdf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557359-20201029.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中原地產公布，第3季香港區營業額10.5億元，按季跌近17%，但仍錄得盈利，全線後勤員工可獲發0.3個月花紅，主任級或以上可獲發0.45個月花紅。<br />\n<br />\n中原說，今年首3季後勤共可獲0.89個月花紅，主管級或以上獲1.33個月花紅。自推行花紅發放機制以來，已連續46季發放。<br />\n<br />\n集團估計，今季發展商為追業續將加快推盤，預料第4季每月一手成交量可達1500宗，二手樓價被帶動下有望錄得3-5%升幅。"},{"pid":"e2a290f9bdbe26f17ef7ff268405ab9a04685427","tid":2262974,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:41:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f28b2aed8819710d9347947430af01aa48e5d72","tid":2262974,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e2a290f9bdbe26f17ef7ff268405ab9a04685427","tid":2262974,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:41:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4051107d70efeca8c2bf2252c19e23959d5d50","tid":2262974,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e2a290f9bdbe26f17ef7ff268405ab9a04685427","tid":2262974,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":